Titolo: Dark Deity

Anno: 2021

Descrizione: Dark Deity is a tactical role-playing video game developed by Sword & Axe LLC and published by Freedom Games. It was funded by Kickstarter, and released on June 15, 2021, on the Steam platform for Microsoft Windows. It follows a group of military academy students in a fantasy universe who are suddenly conscripted into the army years prior to their normal graduation due to the onset of war in the kingdom. The game, which is heavily inspired by the Fire Emblem series, garnered positive reviews from critics.
A Nintendo Switch port is scheduled for a release sometime in 2022.